snippet.title: Outlaw Tales Trailer
snippet.description:
Follow us @sandfishgames 
Help us to improve discord https://discord.gg/Z5nSjrR

Welcome to Outlaw Tales.
You are about to begin your journey as an outlaw. It is up to you to chose the type pf life you want to live.
-Multiplayer
-Over 150 events
-Huge map of 3km
-Real time duels between players
-King of the west mode (survival)
-5 skins and more son
-Ambiental music
